Class GoogleHeaders

java.lang.Object
  HttpHeaders
      com.google.api.client.googleapis.GoogleHeaders

public class GoogleHeaders
extends HttpHeaders

HTTP headers for Google API's.

Implementation is not thread-safe.

1.0
